'''Geiseltalsee Solarpark''', also known as Geiseltalsee, is a 4 MWp [[photovoltaic]] [[power plant]] located in [[Merseburg]], [[Germany]].  The power plant was constructed by [[BP Solar]] using 24,864 BP solar modules.  The power station was completed in 2004<ref name="bp pdf">[http://www.deutschebp.de/liveassets/bp_internet/germany/STAGING/home_assets/assets/bp_solar/produktdatenblaetter/referenz_geiseltalsee_092004.pdf Solaranlage Geiseltalsee] (German)</ref><ref name="bp">[http://www.bp.com/genericarticle.do?categoryId=9012794&contentId=3060080  Geiseltalsee - Germany]</ref>

